ygData.messageBody:
Hey all-- I made it to 20 last night, and finally
became Xela Orcbane. Ever since my first death at the
hands of a lowly Faydark Orc Pawn, I have taken up the
cause of the Faydark elves and worked at the
erradication of all orcs from Norrath. <br><br>Ihave a few
more things to do in Antonicus, then back home to
Kelethin, and finally I'll be off to Kunark. I'll probably
be at lvl 21 by the time I get there. BTW-- i picked
up a sweet Shiny Brass Halbeard from a named Orc in
HP. Anyone got a price on it?? <br><br>As for newbie
questions -- who doesn't agree that the $10.00 isn't worth
it? With a new expansion with a new race and class
coming out by the end of the year-- man-- this game
rocks! <br><br>Xela Orcbane<br>Druid of the 20th
season<br>Xev<br><br>/auction WTT Home brewed ale for a tale of courage and
adventure-- send tell please!!!
